This function is a wrapper for the
\href{https://github.com/OpenGene/fastp}{fastp} software to perform quality
control and preprocessing of FASTQ files (paired-end or single-end).

To install fastp on Linux:

\if{html}{\out{<div class="sourceCode bash">}}\preformatted{wget http://opengene.org/fastp/fastp
chmod a+x ./fastp
sudo mv fastp /usr/local/bin/
}\if{html}{\out{</div>}}

For other OS or specific installation instructions, please refer to the
official fastp GitHub repository: \url{https://github.com/OpenGene/fastp}.
